{
  "stem": "17299.7",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he was the one when-- when the [GERMAN] was, where 5,000 Jews in Riga got killed in March 1942.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was in charge then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans were under quite a-- a guard, and you could not go in the courtroom without a pass.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Lieutenant [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Schwartz. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was in that same lawsuit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I met a fellow named Dodd.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was later a senator here from Connecticut.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The father.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I broke his neck too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was involved in [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1964, they were closing the armory in Springfield--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--which was making weapons for the--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then there was somebody else, but I don't know in which case he was involved.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Clancy was his name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a lawyer later on in Springfield.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Case Nine.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ohlendorf.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He admitted in the courtroom that 90,000 Jews got shot under his command.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when Michael Musmanno, the presiding judge, ask him, what would you have done if your mother or sister would have been one of the victims?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He answered, if I had had the order, I would have shot them too.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were very aggressive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they first saw what freedom in the courtroom means, which was never in Germany before.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not that I know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not of one of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Musmanno was very aggressive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He-- here from the United States.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was later on-- on the Pennsylvania Supreme Court.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had no contact with.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No contact.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The media was under control of the military government.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So there is nothing to say about--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had no contact with, because I had a pass and I had to go in a special section.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That the Germans should have been treated like we were treated in a concentration camp, and not like babies.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
